  "articleContent": "<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Resonator Review | Bambooscape &mdash; Qiuyuan</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Former senior agent of Mingting's Internal Security Agency.</span></div>\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Though enmity filled his younger days, loyalty defined his later years. However, scapegoated for a murder, he is now but a blind swordsman wandering the world alone.</span><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1773763200000/t1pfedcr32h5qd19yk-1773803964999.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1773763200000/qamx7ynr01r09wegkv-1773832491713.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"8481\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-zone-id=\"0\" data-line-index=\"1\" data-line=\"true\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1773763200000/2pu4l90h2b8b0kvi76-1773832161039.jpg\" width=\"800\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1773763200000/24oif8wf0hq80ez1la-1773832249020.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"11185\" data-media-source=\"production_G152_en\" data-desc=\"succ\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://hw-media-cdn-mingchao.kurogame.com/object/1773763200000/rfxab